Pacific Ocean & Winchuck River Views Private Upgraded ad date: 10/14/2015 
99323 Winchuck River Road, Brookings Enjoy the gorgeous views from this private 3 bedroom, 2 bath bright and cheerful home on 0.55 acres. Kitchen has granite counter tops and new stainless steel appliances. Upgrades include hardwood floors throughout and new interior paint plus new wrap-around deck. Main yard is an upper bench with beautiful ocean and river views. No. 15274034 $195,000 Laurie Flynn,
